\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694  24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Thus saith the Lord of hosts, As I have said, so it shall be: and as I have purposed, so [the matter] shall remain: }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 25.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  [even] to destroy the Assyrians upon my land, and upon my mountains: and they shall be for trampling; and their yoke shall be taken away from their shoulders. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 26.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  This is the purpose which the Lord has purposed upon the whole earth: and this the hand that is uplifted against all the nations. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 27.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 For what the Holy God has purposed, who shall frustrate? and who shall turn back his uplifted hand? }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 28.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  In the year in which king Achaz died this word came. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 29.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Rejoice not, all ye Philistines, because the yoke of 
him that smote you is broken: for out of the seed of the serpent shall come forth the young asps, and their young shall come forth flying serpents, }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 30.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 And the poor shall be fed by him, and poor men shall rest in peace: but he shall destroy thy seed with hunger, and shall destroy thy remnant. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 31.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Howl, ye gates of cities; let the cities be troubled and cry, [even] all the Philistines: for smoke is coming from the north, and there is no [possibility] of living. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 32.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 And what shall the kings of the nations answer? That the Lord has founded Sion, and by him the poor of the people shall be saved. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
\par }\pard \s21\qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
