 A righteous son is born for life: but the persecution of the ungodly ends in death. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 20.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Perverse ways are an abomination to the Lord: but all they that are blameless in their ways are acceptable to him. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that unjustly strikes hands shall not be unpu
nished: but he that sows righteousness shall receive a faithful reward. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  As an ornament in a swine's snout, so is beauty to an ill-minded woman. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 23.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  All the desire of the righteous is good: but the hope of the ungodly shall perish. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 There are some who scatter their own, and make it more: and there are some also who gather, yet have less. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Every sincere soul is blessed: but a passionate man is not graceful. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 26.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  May he that hoards corn leave it to the nation: but blessing be on the head of him that gives it. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 27.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that devises good counsels seeks good favor: but as for him that seeks after evil, evil shall overtake him. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 28.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that trusts in wealth shall fall; but he that helps righteous men shall rise. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 29.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that deals not graciously with his own h
ouse shall inherit the wind; and the fool shall be servant to the wise man. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 30.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Out of the fruit of righteousness grows a tree of life; but the souls of transgressors are cut off before their time. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 31.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  If the righteous scarcely be saved, where shall the un
godly and the sinner appear? }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 1.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that loves instruction loves sense, but he that hates reproofs is a fool. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 2.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that has found favor with the Lord is made better; but a transgressor shall be passed over in silence. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 3.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A man shall not prosper by wickedne
ss; but the roots of the righteous shall not be taken up. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A virtuous woman is a crown to her husband; but as a worm in wood, so a bad woman destroys her husband. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  The thoughts of the righteous are true judgments; but ungodly men devise deceits. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 6.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  The
 words of ungodly men are crafty; but the mouth of the upright shall deliver them. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
