\par 
\par }{\cs33\i\f1\fs24\cf6\insrsid15671378 Stichos:}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  God be gracious unto us and bless us, and cause His face to shine upon us and have mercy on us.}{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
