\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  And he drank of the wine, and was drunk, and was naked in his house. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
