 godly gladden the soul, but the works of the ungodly are far from knowledge. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 20.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  If thou walkest with wise men thou shalt be wise: but he that walks with fools shall be known. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Evil shall pursue sinners; but good shall overtake the righteous. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A goo
d man shall inherit children's children; and the wealth of ungodly men is laid up for the just. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 23.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 The righteous shall spend many years in wealth: but the unrighteous shall perish suddenly. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that spares the rod hates his son: but he that loves, carefully chastens him. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A just man eats and satisfies his soul: but the souls of the ungodly are in want. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 1.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Wise women build houses: but a foolish one digs hers down with her hands. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 2.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that walks uprightly fears the Lord; but he that is perverse in his ways shall be dishonored. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 3.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Out of the mouth of fools comes a rod of pride; but the lips of the wise preserve them. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Where no oxen are, the cribs are clean; but where there is abundant produce, the strength of the ox is apparent. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A faithful witness 
does not lie; but an unjust witness kindles falsehoods. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 6.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Thou shalt seek wisdom with bad men, and shalt not find it; but discretion is easily available with the prudent. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
