 The simple believes every word: but the prudent man betakes himself to after-thought. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 A wise man fears, and departs from evil; but the fool trusts in himself, and joins himself with the transgressor. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 17.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A passionate man acts inconsideratel
y; but a sensible man bears up under many things. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 18.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Fools shall have mischief for their portion; but the prudent shall take fast hold of understanding. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 19.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  Evil men shall fall before the good; and the ungodly shall attend at the gates of the righteous. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 20.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 Friends will hate poor friends; but the friends of the rich are many. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  He that dishonors the needy sins: but he that has pity on the poor is most blessed. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  They that go astray devise evils: but the good devise mercy and truth. The framers of evil 
do not understand mercy and truth: but compassion and faithfulness are with the framers of good. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 23.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378 
 With every one who is careful there is abundance: but the pleasure-taking and indolent shall be in want. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 24.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A prudent man is the crown of the wise: but th
e occupation of fools is evil. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 25.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  A faithful witness shall deliver a soul from evil: but a deceitful man kindles falsehoods. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 26.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid15671378  In the fear of the Lord is strong confidence: and he leaves his children a support. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid15671378\charrsid8870694 
